Class IncomingArticleDTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.erp.light.view.dto.IncomingArticleDTO

  • public class IncomingArticleDTO
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a DTO representation of the entity IncomingArticle.
    It is mainly used to transmit data between the frontend and backend.
